Geolocation_permissions_denied.en: The Location permissions can be granted by going to the Settings app, selecting the Privacy option, and then selecting the Location Services option. From here, you can select the website you want to grant permissions to and select the Always option.

Geolocation_permissions_request.en: Dublin Airport user location data to enhance passenger experiences, providing updates throughout their journey and map navigation even when the app is closed or not in use.
